metadata.name: Untitled (root heart) 3/50
metadata.description:
This image is part of a new project in progress. It includes photographs from Killarney Provincial Park, Algonquin in Ontario, and Mont Tremblant in Quebec Canada. The works are being offered as NFTs unlocking the larger high resolution to the purchaser.  Details of the IPFS CID file :

High-resolution original photograph (370.8M tiff 12000 pixels wide 8100 high) 27 inches x 40 inches with 1.25 inch border suitable for printing. Physical prints are available.
